<b>Please answer the following questions to be eligible for admission to Audoroom:</b>:

1. <i>How did you find out about Audoroom?</i>
If it is from a friend/acquaintance who is an existing member of <b>Audoroom</b>, Provide full details of the member (username, full name etc).
if it is from another group, send us a screenshot of the message where Audoroom was mentioned.

2. <i>What are you planning to request?</i> For eg., Ebooks, audiobooks, KU etc.

<i>Your answers are auto-moderated and joining requests are automatically approved if they are deemed fit. 
If you don't answer them properly with all the details, don't expect to be admitted to the group.</i>
